[06/01/2019 02:30:26] <font color="#ffff00">que salen a dar comida gratis,</font>
[06/01/2019 02:30:29] <font color="#ffff00">mientras esperas</font>
[06/01/2019 02:30:29] <font color="#ffff00">para comprar comida.</font>
[06/01/2019 02:30:30] <font color="#ffffff">¿Un café caliente?</font>
